{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectClassProtocol\/installProperties(nPspecs:pspecs:)"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectClassProtocol"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/objectclassprotocol\/installproperties(npspecs:pspecs:)"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Installs new properties from an array of "},{"code":"GParamSpecs","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"installProperties","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"nPspecs","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"pspecs"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp","text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafeMutablePointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GParamSpec"},{"kind":"text","text":">?>!)"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"All properties should be installed during the class initializer.  It","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"is possible to install properties after that, but doing so is not"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"recommend, and specifically, is not guaranteed to be thread-safe vs.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"use of properties on the same type on other threads.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The property id of each property is the index of each "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ParamSpec","type":"reference"},{"text":" in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pspecs"},{"type":"text","text":" array."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The property id of 0 is treated specially by "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and it should not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be used to store a "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ParamSpec","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function should be used if you plan to use a static array of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GParamSpecs"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". For instance, this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"class initialization:","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["typedef enum {","  PROP_FOO = 1,","  PROP_BAR,","  N_PROPERTIES","} MyObjectProperty;","","static GParamSpec *obj_properties[N_PROPERTIES] = { NULL, };","","static void","my_object_class_init (MyObjectClass *klass)","{","  GObjectClass *gobject_class = G_OBJECT_CLASS (klass);","","  obj_properties[PROP_FOO] =","    g_param_spec_int (\"foo\", NULL, NULL,","                      -1, G_MAXINT,","                      0,","                      G_PARAM_READWRITE | G_PARAM_STATIC_STRINGS);","","  obj_properties[PROP_BAR] =","    g_param_spec_string (\"bar\", NULL, NULL,","                         NULL,","                         G_PARAM_READWRITE | G_PARAM_STATIC_STRINGS);","","  gobject_class->set_property = my_object_set_property;","  gobject_class->get_property = my_object_get_property;","  g_object_class_install_properties (gobject_class,","                                     G_N_ELEMENTS (obj_properties),","                                     obj_properties);","}"],"syntax":"C"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"allows calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"type":"text","text":" to notify of property changes:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C","code":["void","my_object_set_foo (MyObject *self, gint foo)","{","  if (self->foo != foo)","    {","      self->foo = foo;","      g_object_notify_by_pspec (G_OBJECT (self), obj_properties[PROP_FOO]);","    }"," }"]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","title":"installProperties(nPspecs:pspecs:)","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"installProperties","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"nPspecs","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pspecs","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp","text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp","text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"GParamSpec","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">?>!)","kind":"text"}],"extendedModule":"GLibObject","externalID":"s:10GLibObject0B13ClassProtocolPAAE17installProperties7nPspecs6pspecsySi_SpySpySo11_GParamSpecVGSgGSgtF"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject